tly double categories, which is\nof independent interest. The graphical description is a consequence of the\nlocal definition. In the special case of a UFC there is also a formalism with\ngroupoid colored graphs. In both cases levels appear when one adds units, which\nclarifies their role in this type of construction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2022 16:11:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
